How to Edit (draw.io + GitHub)
1. Go to: https://app.diagrams.net
2. Click: File -> Open from -> GitHub
3. Log in -> authorize
4. Open: Rhooti-Project -> main -> Milestone2FlowChart.drawio
5. Edit the diagram
6. Press Cmd + S (or Ctrl + S) -> add a short message -> Save

Important 
- Only one person edits at a time
- Always save when done
- Do NOT edit the .drawio file on GitHub (its XML code)

Want to Just View Changes?
- Open:
  - Milestone2FlowChart.jpg
